OL,3,CThief who stole vehicle involved in
OL,4,Cfatal crash jailed
OL,6,FA burglar who stole a vehicle that was
OL,7,Finvolved in a 'horrific' crash that
OL,8,Fkilled a man has been jailed.
OL,10,FPaul Robert Barnes, 33, of Yarm, and
OL,11,Fanother offender broke into a property
OL,12,Fin a village near Northallerton in
OL,13,FJuly 2021 and stole a Polaris off-road
OL,14,Fvehicle.
OL,16,FThe pair took of with the vehicle,
OL,17,Fwith Barnes a passenger, and a 17-year-
OL,18,Fold driving.
