OL,3,CThief who stole vehicle involved in
OL,4,Cfatal crash jailed
OL,6,FThey crossed the A19 at a junction
OL,7,Fnear Thimbleby when they were hit by a
OL,8,Fvan travelling along the A19. Barnes
OL,9,Fmanaged to jump from the vehicle.
OL,11,FThe boy driving the stolen vehicle was
OL,12,Fthrown from it, before being hit by
OL,13,Fanother car. He died from his injuries.
OL,15,FBarnes was arrested and taken to
OL,16,Fhospital with minor injuries. Officers
OL,17,Fsearched him and found a large number
OL,18,Fof class-C opioid drugs.
