OL,3,CThief who stole vehicle involved in
OL,4,Cfatal crash jailed
OL,6,FBarnes pleaded guilty to burglary,
OL,7,Faggravated TWOC (taking a vehicle
OL,8,Fwithout the owner's consent) resulting
OL,9,Fin death and drug possession.
OL,11,FSergeant Marie Williams from North
OL,12,FYorkshire Police said: "This was a
OL,13,Fhorrific incident in which one driver
OL,14,Flost his life and two others will
OL,15,Falways have to live with what happened.
OL,17,F"There are no winners from an
OL,18,Finvestigation like this. But it's
OL,19,Fright that Barnes has been brought to
OL,20,Fjustice and sentenced by the courts
OL,21,Ftoday."
